Source: breakpad-wrapper
Version: 1.0.0
Upstream-URL: https://github.com/rdkcentral/breakpad_wrapper.git
Upstream-Ref: 1.0.0
Build-Depends: breakpad, libbreakpad-dev

Package: breakpad-wrapper
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Depends: breakpad, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: RDK Breakpad wrapper library - runtime
 A C++ wrapper library for Google Breakpad crash reporting system.
 This wrapper simplifies the integration of Breakpad into RDK applications
 by providing a simplified interface for exception handling and crash dump
 generation.
 .
 This package contains the runtime library.

Package: libbreakpad-wrapper-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: breakpad-wrapper (= ${version})
Description: RDK Breakpad wrapper library - development files
 A C++ wrapper library for Google Breakpad crash reporting system.
 This wrapper simplifies the integration of Breakpad into RDK applications.
 .
 This package contains the development headers and static libraries needed
 to build applications using the breakpad wrapper library.
